# Logs
logs
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*
lerna-debug.log*

# Project uses bun; npm/yarn/pnpm lockfiles must not be committed.
# A stray package-lock.json at the repo root confuses Dependabot (opens
# npm-ecosystem PRs that leave bun.lock out of sync) and Next.js workspace
# detection in docs-site/.
package-lock.json
yarn.lock
pnpm-lock.yaml

node_modules
dist
dist-ssr
*.local

