# `src-tauri/vendor/iroh-blobs` is a git submodule (see .gitmodules) pinning
# our fork at github.com/UniClipboard/iroh-blobs. Negate the generic
# `vendor/` rule so submodule state shows up in `git status`.
!src-tauri/vendor/
